{"about_the_game":"This is a simple and complex puzzle game about light. <br>You need to use Optical components to direct lights and lit up the rings.<br><br><strong>Characteristics of light:</strong><br>\u25cf Light travels in a straight line<br>\u25cf Accordant with the Fresnel reflection<br>\u25cf Accordant with the principle of three primary colors<br>\u25cf Light travels at 299,792,458 m/s<br><br><strong>Function of Optical components:</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914090/extras/1.png?t=1720189362\" /><strong>Mirror</strong> - to reflect light<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914090/extras/3.png?t=1720189362\" /><strong>Converter</strong> - to change the frequency of light and hence change its color<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914090/extras/4.png?t=1720189362\" /><strong>Filter</strong> - Can only be passed through by the light of the same color<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914090/extras/2.png?t=1720189362\" /><strong>Prism</strong> - to divide or gather light (not optical dispersion)<br><br><br>The ring will be lit up when light of the same color passes through.<br>You solve the puzzle by lighting up all rings.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914090/extras/game.png?t=1720189362\" /><br><br>After you solve the puzzle, the distribution of the performance of the community (number of prisms they use) will be shown to you. <br>You can choose to optimize your solution or move on.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914090/extras/chart.png?t=1720189362\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game control:</h2><strong>Left mouse button</strong> - to pi